<p class="courseblockdesc">
Systematic approach to the design process. Creative problem solving. Design methodology and engineering principles applied to open-ended design problems with inherent breadth and innovation. Course Information: Same as <a href="/search/?P=IE%20394" title="IE&#160;394" class="bubblelink code" onclick="return showCourse(this, 'IE 394');">IE&#160;394</a>. Credit is not given for <a href="/search/?P=ME%20394" title="ME&#160;394" class="bubblelink code" onclick="return showCourse(this, 'ME 394');">ME&#160;394</a> if the student has credit for <a href="/search/?P=ME%20396" title="ME&#160;396" class="bubblelink code" onclick="return showCourse(this, 'ME 396');">ME&#160;396</a> or <a href="/search/?P=IE%20396" title="IE&#160;396" class="bubblelink code" onclick="return showCourse(this, 'IE 396');">IE&#160;396</a>. Prerequisite(s): Senior standing or above; or approval of the department.<br />
