<p class="courseblockdesc">
Systematic approach to the design process. Creative problem solving. Design methodology and engineering principles applied to open-ended design problems with inherent breadth and innovation. Course Information: Same as <a href="/search/?P=IE%20396" title="IE&#160;396" class="bubblelink code" onclick="return showCourse(this, 'IE 396');">IE&#160;396</a>. Credit is not given for <a href="/search/?P=ME%20396" title="ME&#160;396" class="bubblelink code" onclick="return showCourse(this, 'ME 396');">ME&#160;396</a> if the student has credit in <a href="/search/?P=IE%20444" title="IE&#160;444" class="bubblelink code" onclick="return showCourse(this, 'IE 444');">IE&#160;444</a> or <a href="/search/?P=ME%20444" title="ME&#160;444" class="bubblelink code" onclick="return showCourse(this, 'ME 444');">ME&#160;444</a> or <a href="/search/?P=IE%20445" title="IE&#160;445" class="bubblelink code" onclick="return showCourse(this, 'IE 445');">IE&#160;445</a> or <a href="/search/?P=ME%20445" title="ME&#160;445" class="bubblelink code" onclick="return showCourse(this, 'ME 445');">ME&#160;445</a>. Prerequisite(s): <a href="/search/?P=ME%20347" title="ME&#160;347" class="bubblelink code" onclick="return showCourse(this, 'ME 347');">ME&#160;347</a>; or <a href="/search/?P=IE%20345" title="IE&#160;345" class="bubblelink code" onclick="return showCourse(this, 'IE 345');">IE&#160;345</a>. Open only to seniors. Class Schedule Information: To be properly registered, students must enroll in one Laboratory and one Lecture-Discussion.<br />
